title: Nearly 40 years later, 'Stranger Things' boosts Kate Bush's music worldwide
description: In this World Cafe session from 1993, Kate Bush spoke with original host David Dye about a range of subjects: from her ambitions to working with Prince to being an Elton John fan as a teenager.
